# FomaPrint environment variables
# Copy to `.env.local` and fill in. All values are optional for local dev.
#
# Lead capture (custom-order + reseller-application forms) fans out to three
# FREE channels — no paid email service required:
#   1. SMTP email   — your own mailbox (e.g. info@fomaprint.com). Sends a branded
#                     notice to the inbox WITH the lead attached as a .csv, plus
#                     a confirmation to the applicant.
#   2. CSV webhook  — optional cumulative CSV/Sheet: POSTs each lead to a URL you
#                     control (e.g. a Google Apps Script that appends a row you
#                     can export as CSV).
#   3. Server log   — always on; every lead prints as a "[LEAD]" line (recover
#                     with `vercel logs`). Safety net so a lead is never lost.
# A form shows an error to the visitor only when a configured channel (1 or 2)
# was attempted and all configured ones failed.

# --- SMTP (free email via your own mailbox) ---------------------------------
# Works with any provider that gives you SMTP for info@fomaprint.com — e.g.
# Zoho Mail (free custom-domain plan), your domain host's mail, or a Gmail/
# Workspace app password. Copy the 3 values from your mail provider's SMTP page.
SMTP_HOST=smtp.zoho.com
SMTP_PORT=587
SMTP_USER=info@fomaprint.com
SMTP_PASS=
# Optional: force TLS. Auto-detected (true when SMTP_PORT=465) if left unset.
# SMTP_SECURE=false

# From address shown on outgoing email. Defaults to "FomaPrint <SMTP_USER>".
EMAIL_FROM="FomaPrint <info@fomaprint.com>"

# Inbox that receives new custom-order / reseller-application notifications
# (with the lead CSV attached). Defaults to the brand inbox when unset.
EMAIL_TO=info@fomaprint.com

# --- CSV webhook (optional cumulative list) ---------------------------------
# Any HTTPS endpoint that accepts a JSON POST of the lead — e.g. a Google Apps
# Script web app that appends a row to a Sheet (download as CSV anytime).
# Payload: { "kind": "custom-order"|"seller-application", "at": <ISO>, ...fields }
LEAD_WEBHOOK_URL=

# --- Site -------------------------------------------------------------------
# Public canonical site URL — used for metadata, sitemap, robots and OG tags.
NEXT_PUBLIC_SITE_URL=https://foma-design.vercel.app
